# Keep host build artifacts and dependencies OUT of the Docker build context. They are
# platform-specific and must be (re)built inside the image:
#  - node_modules built on the host (e.g. Ubuntu/glibc) carry the wrong native binaries for the
#    Alpine/musl builder (e.g. @rollup/rollup-linux-x64-musl is missing) -> `ng build` fails.
#    Excluding it forces a fresh, platform-correct `npm ci` in the builder stage.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.angular
**/coverage

# Backend build output (the image builds the jar fresh).
target
**/target

# VCS / IDE / local runtime noise
.git
.gitignore
.idea
*.iml
logs
db
*.log
